title: The Guide to Building a Social Circle and Killing it on Instagram w/ @reel_daddy
description:
Ready to level up your social life and Instagram game? You won't want to miss this episode. We're sitting down with @reel_daddy the guru of hosting epic parties and a wizard on social media. He's gonna spill the tea on how he went from military event planning to becoming an Instagram sensation. Whether you're looking to make new friends, host insane parties, or kill it on Instagram, this episode is your golden ticket. Tune in and get the lowdown on how to do it all.

Show Notes:

02:39 - "@REEL_DADDY" - Find out how our guest earned the name! 

04:38 - From NYC to Austin! - Find out why our guest moved!

06:15 - "How did you set up your new social circle?" - Listen to how our guest had to adapt and meet new people in new places! 

09:34 - "I was more about meeting people at events" - Find out when our host started hosting parties!

12:17 - I learned how to plan and put events together in the military! - Find out where our guest got his skills from originally!

13:25 - Is it harder to make women show up at events? - Find out here! 

15:39 - The tipping point! - Find out when our guest reached his prime with hosting parties and how it took off! 

17:56 - The process of organizing a great event! - Find out step by step! 

19:41 - What do people get wrong when hosting events?? - Find out here! 

22:02 - "Did you ever flop a party/event?" - Find out here! 

24:06 - 'Show up rate anxiety' and how to deal with it! - Listen here! 

26:20 - "I just did it for me" - Learn how our guest started filming his parties!

30:22 - "@REEL_DADDY" - Looking through our guest's Instagram and his thoughts behind the algorithm! 

32:50 - Banger video examples! - Guest shares his reels and runs us through his process and thoughts!

34:29 - "What is the filming/editing process like?" - Our guest runs us through the process with golden tips! 

38:37 - "A lot of your filming style is moving the camera around!" - Guest shares secret filming techniques that will improve your game! 

42:30 - "You do everything on Instagram?" - Find out here! 

43:12 - "2-3 hours or sitting on it for a day" - Find out how long the process takes! 

44:41 - Instagram covers... - Guest spills his secrets and gives killer IG cover tips! 

45:51 - "Everyone tells me to post on TikTok" - Find out how our guest handles other socials, and our host speculates about the secret TikTok algorithm! 

51:51 - Business and social media... Mix together or separate? - Find out our take on it! 

54:08 - Watch @REEL_DADDY's hilarious comedy skit! - Watch here! 

57:03 - Comedy skits VS Party reels, what is HARDER? - Guest breaks it down! 

57:51 - "What has come from all of this?" - Guest shares his accomplishments from doing his reels and skits!

01:01:37 - "Are woman more interested in you now?" - Find out if it makes a difference!

01:02:33 - "Don't put me in your video!" - Guest shares if he experiences any resistance when filming his reels! 

01:05:59 - Do you want to be like @REEL_DADDY? - Here is some advice from the man himself! 

01:09:14 - What's next for @REEL_DADDY? - Listen here!
